
                                            The 63-year-old was shot at by unknown gunmen travelling in a white minibus taxi on Thursday afternoon.
                                         CAPE TOWN - A man has been shot dead along Voortrekker Road near the Bellville Civic Centre. The 63-year-old was shot at by unknown gunmen travelling in a white minibus taxi on Thursday afternoon. The police’s Noloyiso Rwexana said: “According to reports a 63-year-old man was shot and fatally wounded by unidentified suspects in a white Toyota Quantum. No one has been arrested at this stage.”